title: Sean Patrick Maloney on His Loss, the Media and A.O.C.
description: Mr. Maloney said that he and other New York Democrats were unable to overcome suburban fears of crime. He also had some harsh words for Representative Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez.
dc:creator: Nicholas Fandos
media:credit: Kenny Holston for The New York Times
media:description: Representative Sean Patrick Maloney said that Gov. Kathy Hochul's struggles in the suburbs hurt Democratic candidates in those areas.
